,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:43:06.000Z","msg":"我都掛住大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f15d12ac9f96c6c42c6fa9bbbbb094b3aa4f1b","tid":1056624,"uid":199617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e4b7f80a20f9aef5aa2def9a40d4f34066be2902","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90d1a75f660fce47c39c980c10f42cc68523d4c2","tid":1056624,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T12:57:31.000Z","msg":"上大學當然要瘋狂目及女，重要專登坐係啲女隔離當面咁目及，寧做痴漢，不做"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:49:25.000Z","msg":"質素高嘅唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:50:22.000Z","msg":"梗係，邊及星澄咁高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6dc94266cf55cbc4b898ab49cc03744c6b4a64f","tid":1056624,"uid":46486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:53:46.000Z","msg":"留名先 之後再睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71d3eead2cfca249505cd97001915bb4c93e148","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11f15d12ac9f96c6c42c6fa9bbbbb094b3aa4f1b","tid":1056624,"uid":199617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e4b7f80a20f9aef5aa2def9a40d4f34066be2902","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90d1a75f660fce47c39c980c10f42cc68523d4c2","tid":1056624,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T12:57:31.000Z","msg":"上大學當然要瘋狂目及女，重要專登坐係啲女隔離當面咁目及，寧做痴漢，不做"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:49:25.000Z","msg":"質素高嘅唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:50:22.000Z","msg":"梗係，邊及星澄咁高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T00:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808cb795f9a9e49980dd874e5976185505d2a65b","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6dc94266cf55cbc4b898ab49cc03744c6b4a64f","tid":1056624,"uid":46486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:53:46.000Z","msg":"留名先 之後再睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T00:57:41.000Z","msg":"歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4022077afe608494bfac55dd92c7a62e94d8b03","tid":1056624,"uid":169231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T02:05:44.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0184db406efc7dcb26b225b3a8dd894a80de54b6","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4022077afe608494bfac55dd92c7a62e94d8b03","tid":1056624,"uid":169231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T02:05:44.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T02:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120488ac045030e5f333dfac654546eee4acff0c","tid":1056624,"uid":110468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:43:16.000Z","msg":"脱毒學會入面全會唔會有囡囡出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n LM <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b34bd0afc209edeabc81ae59a33c79b4fbe987","tid":1056624,"uid":18899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T04:00:31.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"3393a8eece5e464ee307fa335019596f01a589af","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"120488ac045030e5f333dfac654546eee4acff0c","tid":1056624,"uid":110468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:43:16.000Z","msg":"脱毒學會入面全會唔會有囡囡出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n LM <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:07:45.000Z","msg":"現實只會係一班毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb35a5a47a75ed93717caa0982dfcc651a540a5b","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6b34bd0afc209edeabc81ae59a33c79b4fbe987","tid":1056624,"uid":18899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T04:00:31.000Z","msg":"LM"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T05:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0789e9384d07c58453e2f4e750b46726e7b533","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T09:05:33.000Z","msg":"上堂又打咗啲，繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就喺我繼續摺喺後樓梯，食緊未食完嘅雞軟骨炒飯嗰陣，樓上又傳嚟一吓開門聲。<br />\n<br />\n唔係啩？又返嚟？<br />\n<br />\n想安安樂樂食餐飯都唔得，學校呢個地方，年中都唔知迫死幾多毒撚&hellip;但我必須澄清，我唔係毒撚，真係唔係架，因為我&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n突然之間，喉嚨一陣異樣感覺，我feel 到有啲嘢噎咗落去。<br />\n<br />\n「咳&mdash;&mdash;咳&mdash;&mdash;咳&mdash;&mdash;」舊雞軟骨卡住喺喉嚨唔上唔落咁，咳極都嘔唔返出嚟，慢慢我愈來愈抖唔到氣&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n唔通我要死喺大學後樓梯？<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候我聽到天使嚟接我嘅聲音：「你冇嘢嘛？」<br />\n<br />\n「咳&mdash;&mdash;咳&mdash;&mdash;」我依然喺度咳，乜都講唔到。<br />\n<br />\n但我擘大眼一睇，原來唔係天使嚟接我，只係一個陌生嘅女仔。<br />\n<br />\n佢見我講唔到野，好似get到我噎親，於是開始有節奏咁打我背脊：「慢慢嚟、123、123&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n唔知佢個方法係咪真係有用，總之過咗幾秒喉嚨裡面舊雞軟骨就俾我吐返出嚟，仲要飛越十幾級樓梯，跌咗落下一層。<br />\n<br />\n「唔該晒&hellip;&hellip;」我補上一句。<br />\n<br />\n個女仔聽到，咩都冇講，我地就咁dead air ，你眼望我眼。<br />\n<br />\n我只感覺到一陣尷尬，想即刻走。<br />\n<br />\n點知佢突然問：「同學，你係咪自己一個喺度食飯呢？」<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候我先望清楚佢&hellip;哇，粉紅色頭髮嘅？五官望落唔多似本地人，加上一身JK制服打扮，佢可能係一個cosplayer 。<br />\n<br />\n我立即坐開一個身位。<br />\n<br />\n「同學，你係咪自己一個人食飯呢？」佢又問多次。<br />\n<br />\n我從來冇諗過有人會咁直接問，所以一時啞咗，唔通答佢係咩&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n「你寂寞嗎？」見我唔答，佢又問。<br />\n<br />\n怪人，果然無緣無故會走入大學後樓梯嘅人，除咗清潔姐姐之外都係怪人，包括我。<br />\n<br />\n我選擇繼續無視佢，反正唔該又講咗，望吓隻錶，都差唔多夠鐘上下一堂&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n「&hellip;等陣先呀，我啲對白都未講晒！」個女仔見到我起身，即刻想攔住我嘅去路。<br />\n<br />\n「&hellip;對白？」<br />\n<br />\n佢無視我嘅提問，繼續自顧自說：「少年，你想要脫毒嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n「痴線。」我忍唔住，低聲講咗一句。<br />\n<br />\n「如果想嘅話，就來找我吧，我會在soc 房等你。」我冇聽錯，佢真係夾雜咗啲書面語喺句嘢入面&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n然後，佢喺書包入面拎咗張單張塞俾我，就開門飄走咗，我用個飄字，係因為佢真係飄架，頭先望一望佢對腳，先知佢著住一對roller 鞋&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n估唔到讀到大學都有人中二病未好返&mdash;&mdash;呢個係我對嗰個女仔嘅結論，中二病我見得多，中二到呢個程度真係第一次見&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n少年？佢當自己喺漫畫入面走出嚟咩&hellip;真係得啖笑。<br />\n<br />\n我冷笑咗幾吓，望一望手佢頭先塞俾我嘅單張，上面寫住：<br />\n<br />\n少年，你想要脫毒嗎？<br />\n脫毒學會歡迎你！<br />\n隨時來找我們吧～<br />\n<br />\n原來咁都可以整個學會？咁其實我都可以整個毒撚&hellip;吖唔係，係孤高學會先啱，咁就打正旗號有soc房俾我柄埋喇。<br />\n<br />\n睬佢都嘥氣&hellip;我將張紙掉落垃圾桶，慢慢就唔記得咗呢件事。"},{"pid":"b61b93e78ab3ecc6e19df3281faa0ef6e48e8804","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T09:07:55.000Z","msg":"題外話，呢個故事同我上一個post風格好唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上個post我打到某啲位其實鬱咗好耐先打得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望今次一路輕輕鬆鬆打落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1338b99e7efa7492fd2778b4d36f68008b7131a9","tid":1056624,"uid":107249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:44:10.000Z","msg":"正正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9123f7ffe24972fe7ae2659a7a0403cb6e3300a4","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:52:30.000Z","msg":"之後嗰幾日，我如常自己一個人上落堂，除咗有一日為咗科Common core 而去到晒銀時地頭上堂，仲因為咁而撞到幾個禮拜冇見嘅舊相識。<br />\n<br />\n「喂，好耐冇見。」佢拍拍我膊頭同我講。<br />\n<br />\n「你都知好耐冇見喇咩？」<br />\n<br />\n佢叫梁成樂，係我由中一識到而家嘅好朋友，我地入同一間大學，但係唔同科，加上佢入u後充分展現出佢嘅現充本性，上莊住Hall 飯飯撈，搞到我地都冇乜時間見面，搵佢食飯難過登天。<br />\n<br />\n「唔好講啲咁嘅嘢啦，今日難得我得閒，一齊食個tea。」<br />\n<br />\n我冇講啲咩，好自然就跟佢走咗去canteen 。<br />\n<br />\n叫完嘢食坐低之後，佢一嚟就問：「點呀你最近？」<br />\n<br />\n「&hellip;咪又係咁。」<br />\n<br />\n「又係咁毒咁摺？」佢打咗個突咁講。<br />\n<br />\n「你第一日識我咩？」我反問佢，佢由識我開始就應該知道我唔習慣主動識人、唔習慣參加social 活動，但我堅持自己唔係毒！係孤高！係不可親近！所以我向佢澄清：「仲有，我呢啲唔係叫毒&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n點知喺我講落去之前，俾佢截住：「係孤高吖嘛，好心你聽吓你條女講，識多啲人啦&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n俾佢咁樣講一講，我心裡一沉，對住碟炸雞脾都食唔落，唔係因為啲乜嘢，而係因為佢提起一個唔應該提起嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n一路以嚟我堅持自己唔係毒撚，冇乜特別原因，只因為我唔係A0，我有個由中學畢業就開始拍拖嘅女朋友，佢叫林星澄。雖然我覺得自己性格係毒，但為免俾人話偽毒可恥，所以我要重申多次，我唔係毒撚，係孤高先啱。<br />\n<br />\n講返我女朋友，我地又係一齊升上呢間u，讀埋同一科，於是我地渡過一個好美妙嘅sem 1，但開心嘅時間總係過得好快，sem 2一開始佢同我講佢要去exchange，我當時打咗個突：<br />\n<br />\n「year 1去咩exchange 呀？」<br />\n<br />\n「year 1唔去得exchange 架咩？」佢當時咁答我。<br />\n<br />\n「&hellip;&hellip;得。」<br />\n<br />\n「你都得架，你肯識多啲人，睇多啲個世界嘅話。」<br />\n<br />\n我依舊敷衍回應：「&hellip;哦，知喇。」<br />\n<br />\n「你成日都話知，都係得個講字&hellip;」從語氣中可以聽出佢有所不滿，加上我之前應承過佢努力讀書，點知sem 1 gpa 完美地唔過2，所以佢可能有啲嬲我。<br />\n<br />\n「你都知我性格架啦，我每次識人同玩活動都要好大勇氣架。」我懶係輕鬆咁講，想氹佢笑返。<br />\n<br />\n點知佢笑都唔笑，仲係木口木臉：「藉口。」<br />\n<br />\n嗰刻我就知道，今次可能有啲大鑊。<br />\n<br />\n結果直到佢飛之前，佢都未嬲完，我唔知隔咗咁耐佢嬲完未，但係我搵佢佢有覆嘅，簡單地覆咁囉。<br />\n<br />\n例如佢飛嘅第一晚，我問佢到咗未。<br />\n<br />\n佢簡單回答「到咗」兩隻字。<br />\n<br />\n又例如我問佢日本有咩好食，佢回「好多」。<br />\n<br />\n整整吓我都唔敢搵佢喇，對上一次同佢對話已經係一個禮拜之前。"},{"pid":"3bd003f1852955691f1695ed12dc5c71d6347504","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1338b99e7efa7492fd2778b4d36f68008b7131a9","tid":1056624,"uid":107249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:44:10.000Z","msg":"正正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1206b25557524ae334986b05682ab370a1dd36ec","tid":1056624,"uid":224452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T00:40:11.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"102c762d71a37e7ca075db817f6ba84c6ab00723","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1206b25557524ae334986b05682ab370a1dd36ec","tid":1056624,"uid":224452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T00:40:11.000Z","msg":"lm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T01:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ccde888d912e446c264f29a58d1be73cf4e7a7","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T01:39:45.000Z","msg":"「所以星澄走咗之後，你毒到匿喺後樓梯食飯？」樂仔一路据眼前個炸脾，一路用慌死其他人聽唔到嘅聲線講。<br />\n<br />\n「我都唔想架&hellip;咁我之前日日同佢一齊食架嘛&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「條女走咗你就唔識食飯，你都得架喇&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「&hellip;唔想俾其他人見到我一個人食。」<br />\n<br />\n「咁你咪搵Cayden 囉屌。」樂仔好勞氣咁講。<br />\n<br />\n嚟到呢度又要停一停，佢口中嘅Cayden 又係同我同一間中學升上嚟嘅朋友，不過佢最近好似研究緊佛學，學緊咩禁食嗰啲，仲叫我食飯唔使預佢。<br />\n<br />\n我照直同樂仔解釋，但佢永遠唔會明白孤高者嘅心理：「我都係唔明你匿喺後樓梯做乜鳩&hellip;自己一個食飯究竟有咩問題&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n我都答唔出，不過就係唔想俾人見到，可能將來我會有夠膽自己一個坐canteen 嘅一日，但絕對唔係而家。<br />\n<br />\n「講到尾都係因為你太毒。」樂仔總結一句。<br />\n<br />\n「我都話我唔係&hellip;&hellip;」我想辯駁之際，又俾佢打斷：「唔係得我咁講架，星澄都係咁講架。」<br />\n<br />\n講完之後，佢隊部電話俾我睇，上面係佢同星澄啲對話記錄，佢地似乎談論緊我。<br />\n<br />\n你同你男朋友冷戰緊？&nbsp; 19：28<br />\n<br />\n呢條係樂仔發出去嘅，日期應該係星澄走咗冇幾耐我向佢呻嗰日。<br />\n<br />\n冇呀&nbsp; 21：20<br />\n<br />\n佢好似以為你嬲佢 21：21<br />\n<br />\n星澄再回嗰陣已經係隔晚嘅凌晨，仲要係長篇大論：<br />\n<br />\n我係有嬲佢呀，邊個叫佢成日應承完啲嘢又唔做，我叫佢比啲心機讀書，你知唔知佢最後gpa連2都冇呀，我叫佢識多啲人，佢次次都哦完就算，有冇真係試過去識多啲人？仲有我成日叫佢玩多啲活動，佢總有藉口話唔啱自己，入到u之後成個退步晒，問佢乜嘢都話唔知是但，以前讀中學唔係咁架&hellip;&nbsp; 02：56<br />\n<br />\n咁佢對你好唔好？ 03：00<br />\n<br />\n然後又係星澄嘅回覆：<br />\n<br />\n好，但我唔鍾意佢咁毒&nbsp; 5：58<br />\n<br />\n我望住呢句句子，終於明白咩叫跌落深淵嘅絕望。<br />\n<br />\n我唔鍾意佢咁毒<br />\n我唔鍾意佢咁毒<br />\n我唔鍾意佢咁毒<br />\n<br />\n佢唔鍾意我咁毒&hellip;&hellip;佢出到聲話我毒&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;佢會唔會同我分手？<br />\n<br />\n喺我驚魂未定嘅時候，樂仔碌開ig俾我睇，我認得個account ，係同星澄一齊去日本exchange 嘅某個女同學。<br />\n<br />\n佢post咗好多同嗰邊啲日本仔嘅合照。<br />\n<br />\n樂仔一路碌ig一路講：「你睇吓啲日本仔個個青靚白淨，我諗你再唔脫吓毒，就準備孤獨過完呢四年啦。」<br />\n<br />\n佢呢一句，直頭將我打落更深嘅深淵。<br />\n<br />\n我突然間覺得好飽，飽到想嘔返頭先啲雞脾出嚟，於是講咗句：「&hellip;我唔食喇。」然後垂頭喪氣咁離開咗canteen ，臨走前聽到樂仔細細聲講咗句：「死火&hellip;唔通講得太過份？」<br />\n<br />\n但我已經咩都聽唔入耳，腦裡充斥住嗰句：我唔鍾意佢咁毒。"},{"pid":"892a253721eee04da5d3aa0fb415eb64d66f5c88","tid":1056624,"uid":110468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T01:49:26.000Z","msg":"星澄會唔會被架仔溝左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Molamola<br />\n<br />\n正正喺時候脱毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1606b4edf3561d3983496eae2f4c48f71b1a3cef","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"892a253721eee04da5d3aa0fb415eb64d66f5c88","tid":1056624,"uid":110468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T01:49:26.000Z","msg":"星澄會唔會被架仔溝左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Molamola<br />\n<br />\n正正喺時候脱毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T03:10:52.000Z","msg":"做現充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c11f6addc304a9d4073d05b34790937bc5c27b","tid":1056624,"uid":224452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:34:08.000Z","msg":"更得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a32685969b76139daac95137c0af8985652f55a","tid":1056624,"uid":199617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:19:41.000Z","msg":"星澄嗰part係咪真㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過主角又真係毒過頭，要加油呀正正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cfff3ce1bde7061f21037938ff783e67a8f29d0","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4c11f6addc304a9d4073d05b34790937bc5c27b","tid":1056624,"uid":224452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:34:08.000Z","msg":"更得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:04:40.000Z","msg":"冇野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e296b661209c33d0597f2887248eb3d8cd56fc","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a32685969b76139daac95137c0af8985652f55a","tid":1056624,"uid":199617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:19:41.000Z","msg":"星澄嗰part係咪真㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過主角又真係毒過頭，要加油呀正正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:04:52.000Z","msg":"假架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813203521215ee476830a2f2643b159e8895a6ae","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:36:56.000Z","msg":"而家睇返突然覺得個標題好膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e2b873bdd42670f227f28783f2c90c71a23cba","tid":1056624,"uid":224452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"813203521215ee476830a2f2643b159e8895a6ae","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:36:56.000Z","msg":"而家睇返突然覺得個標題好膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:51:34.000Z","msg":"歡迎加入NHK！"},{"pid":"15932c17b845bc1bc6916090ab53ae178c448dcd","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21e2b873bdd42670f227f28783f2c90c71a23cba","tid":1056624,"uid":224452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"813203521215ee476830a2f2643b159e8895a6ae","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:36:56.000Z","msg":"而家睇返突然覺得個標題好膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:51:34.000Z","msg":"歡迎加入NHK！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cceac3235a165f4c7e9e412192830ff5f153465","tid":1056624,"uid":142378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"如果當初冇我個fd同我一齊讀 我就同孤高嘅主角一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個fd都話我咩活動都唔參加好毒好摺"},{"pid":"152432c380b0d22c2ee694e75574777c3d355953","tid":1056624,"uid":199700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T17:18:38.000Z","msg":"咁快爛尾?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca1c02145db558745b4ed5713e62008a5d6b304","tid":1056624,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"152432c380b0d22c2ee694e75574777c3d355953","tid":1056624,"uid":199700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T17:18:38.000Z","msg":"咁快爛尾?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T05:08:43.000Z","msg":"...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eba3aa8d8888c4d3378092f3ccdac18c7afd575","tid":1056624,"uid":237914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尾</span></span>"},{"pid":"c71713e35677e39c5147a414170d98c13ee7d606","tid":1056624,"uid":237914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T05:53:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">已</span></span>"}]}